year U.S. dollar-denominated debt in a benchmark offering,
according to a person familiar with the transaction.  The senior unsecured notes may be sold as soon as today,
said the person, who declined to be identified because terms
arenâ€™t set. Proceeds may be used for the repayment of existing
debt and for general corporate purposes, the person said. A
